                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>No. 3719</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(center)\">OFFICE OF THE CHIEF RABBI.</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>London</placeName>, <date>August 1<hi rend=\"sup\"\n                        >st</hi> 5622</date></p>\n            <p>Revd &amp; Dear Sir/</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">I have yet<lb/> to express my sincere thanks to<lb/> you for your\n                very kind congratulations<lb/> on my son's promotion. I hope<lb/> with his talents\n                he will prove an<lb/> able &amp; zealous worker in the vine-<lb/>yard of the Lord.\n                He has as yet,<lb/> much to learn &amp; to study—but<lb/> at a later period I think\n                he<lb/> will contribute to your paper.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Concerning your affairs with<lb/> your agent, <persName>Mr John\n                    Joel</persName> I<lb/> have made accurate inquiries.<lb/> He had been insured in\n                the Alliance</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3fx74j4r/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
